name: TRIPLE FUSION
description:
FreeTees is a design mark from Olomouc (Czech Republic). 
Our T-shirts are printed by digital printing technique (Kornit)

Men´s T-Shirts are made of 100% Cotton 
Women´s T-Shirts are made of Cotton and Elasten combination.

Washing gently from the back at 40°C, do not iron over the image.

All shown motifs are available also as a desktop graphic and prints. 
If are you interested in it, please ask me for details. 

designed by (c) pavel hrubisek / freetees
